         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Private Secretary's Office ¶ 8th March 1866 ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I am directed by The Governor to inform you in answer to your letter that His Excellency much regrets that having fully enquired into all the ci...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">66.03.08</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Henry Warde</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Unit 2, pp. 163-4, VPRS 1092 Governor's letter books, VA 466 Governor, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">Transcribed 9.8.93. To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">Link to M's approach letter. Look in registers at PRO. What was the Anderson case?</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Private Secretary's Office</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">8th March 1866</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am directed by The Governor to inform you in answer to your letter that His Excellency much regrets that having fully enquired into all the circumstances connected with Andersons case and antecedents he does not feel justified in extending to him the pardon you solicit.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am desired also to state that it is impossible to obtain effectual legal security that he will never return to the Colony and His Excellency has on that account already refused to grant a pardon in cases where that consideration was more deserved than in Andersons</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I have etc</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>(sd) H. L. Warde</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr Mueller FRS</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanical Gardens</p>
